original_title: Mysterious Doctor Satan Return of the Copperhead
overview: Return of the Copperhead: Doctor Satan's henchman remotely blows up the experimental ship, with Lois and crew aboard, as ordered.
tagline: CRAZED WITH THE LUST TO KILL! A power-mad maniac unleashes a lightning attack on an unsuspecting nation...And finds the Copperhead thirsting for revenge!
title: Mysterious Doctor Satan Return of the Copperhead
